items.name: Launch TWAMM Protocol
items.description: Successfully launch the TWAMM protocol with the $1M trade.

description: This proposal outlines the implementation of TWAMM (Time-Weighted Average Market Maker) protocol for Nouns DAO treasury diversification. It presents the advantages, product design, incentives, risks, and competition. The proposal also includes a detailed budget and roadmap for the project.

project.name: TWAMM
project.description: TWAMM is a time-weighted average market maker protocol designed to enable large token swaps on-chain.

title: Treasury Diversification: Swap 500 wstETH -> rETH via TWAMM
